Date: Wed, 4 Mar 2026 20:51:28 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: Razorpay payment integration

- supabase/functions/create-razorpay-order: creates Razorpay order server-side
  so secret key is never exposed to browser
- supabase/functions/razorpay-webhook: verifies HMAC-SHA256 signature,
  updates order status, idempotent (safe against duplicate webhooks)
- CheckoutPage: adds Razorpay as default payment option with widget
  - Loads Razorpay script dynamically
  - Shows UPI/Cards/NetBanking badge
  - Handles payment success and cancellation
  - Falls back to COD/Mock for non-Razorpay payments
